================================================================================
4. EXCLUDED INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY
================================================================================

The following are proprietary, confidential, and are NOT included in this
repository under any circumstance:

  - Firmware source code and build artifacts
  - Mobile application source code
  - PCB layouts, EasyEDA project files, and Gerber outputs
  - Electrical schematics and wiring diagrams
  - Mechanical drawings, CAD models, and STL files
  - Sensor calibration equations, coefficients, and characterization data
  - Control algorithms and their implementations
  - MQTT broker endpoints, topic namespaces, and credentials
  - Wi-Fi provisioning credentials and device keys
  - Any source code excerpt of any subsystem

All descriptions contained in this repository are maintained deliberately at an
architectural level of abstraction and do not constitute an enabling
disclosure.

